{"descriptions":[{"id":327,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp\u003eTraditionally referred to as བྱེད་​​སྒྲ་, literally “agent-sound,” indicates the agent of the action (“by”), the instrument (“with”), the cause (“because of,” “by”), and the manner (“with”); it also marks causal subordinate clauses, in which case it may be translated by “since,” “because,” etc.\u003c/p\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":false,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:07:31 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:07:31 UTC","authors":[{"id":"2","fullname":"David Germano"}]},{"id":328,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eTraditional grammars refer to this mark as \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eབྱེད་སྒྲ་\u003c/span\u003e, literally \u0026ldquo;agent-sound.\u0026rdquo; The agentive indicates the agent of the action (\u0026ldquo;by\u0026rdquo;), the instrument (\u0026ldquo;with\u0026rdquo;), the cause (\u0026ldquo;because of,\u0026rdquo; \u0026ldquo;by\u0026rdquo;), and the manner (\u0026ldquo;with\u0026rdquo;); it also marks causal subordinate clauses, in which case it may be translated by \u0026ldquo;since,\u0026rdquo; \u0026ldquo;because,\u0026rdquo; etc.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe agentive is formed by adding a \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eས\u003c/span\u003e to the genitive. The variants follow the same pattern as in the case of the genitive: \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགིས་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགྱིས་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཀྱིས་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eས་\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eས་\u003c/span\u003e is used after vowels and \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eའ་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགིས་\u003c/span\u003e is used after \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eང་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཀྱིས་\u003c/span\u003e is used after \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eད་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eབ་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eས་\u003c/span\u003e and the \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eད་དྲག་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགྱིས་\u003c/span\u003e is used after \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eན་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eམ་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eར་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eལ་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e \u003c/ul\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eIn Classical Tibetan, vowels may also be followed by the variant \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡིས་\u003c/span\u003e, or even by the more archaic form \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eའིས་\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe following table gives examples of how these variants are used.\u003c/p\u003e \u003ctable border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"\u003e \u003ctbody\u003e \u003ctr\u003e \u003ctd width=\"151\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཉི་མ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Sun\u0026rdquo;\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"144\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཉི་མས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003c/tr\u003e \u003ctr\u003e \u003ctd width=\"151\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརི་མོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Drawing\u0026rdquo;\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"144\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརི་མོས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003c/tr\u003e \u003ctr\u003e \u003ctd width=\"151\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཆུ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Water\u0026rdquo;\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"144\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཆུས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003c/tr\u003e \u003ctr\u003e \u003ctd width=\"151\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eམི་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Man,\u0026rdquo; \u0026ldquo;person\u0026rdquo;\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"144\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eམིས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003c/tr\u003e \u003ctr\u003e \u003ctd width=\"151\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eམེ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Fire\u0026rdquo;\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"144\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eམེས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003c/tr\u003e \u003ctr\u003e \u003ctd width=\"151\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eམདའ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Arrow\u0026rdquo;\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"144\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eམདས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003c/tr\u003e \u003ctr\u003e \u003ctd width=\"151\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eདགེ་རྒན་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Teacher\u0026rdquo;\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"144\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eདགེ་རྒན་གྱིས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003c/tr\u003e \u003ctr\u003e \u003ctd width=\"151\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརྒན་ལགས་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Teacher\u0026rdquo; (H)\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"144\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརྒན་ལགས་ཀྱིས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003c/tr\u003e \u003ctr\u003e \u003ctd width=\"151\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eདྲུང་ཡིག་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Secretary\u0026rdquo;\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"144\" valign=\"top\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eདྲུང་ཡིག་གིས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003c/tr\u003e \u003c/tbody\u003e \u003c/table\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eIn conversation, the three particles \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགིས་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཀྱིས་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགྱིས་\u003c/span\u003e are pronounced in exactly the same way, as an unstressed syllable: gi.\u003c/p\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":true,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:07:31 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:07:31 UTC","authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}]}]}